public static @NotNull java.lang.String[] getCustomBars(@NotNull

        Load the bars from a custom file
        Parameters:
        config - Configuration file from which to retrieve custom bar settings
        Returns:
        An array in which each element represents the bar to be shown based on the corresponding health of the mob. If the element is null, it means that no bar is set (and therefore nothing will be shown).
